{"tid":903743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係呢個時勢,其實應該要用Twitter","createTime":"2018-11-15T19:49:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T01:08:29.000Z","uid":44925,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c57d9da0ec3daa3da094e50b84d1f24140ee063a","tid":903743,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T19:49:31.000Z","msg":"當柒婆不斷出醜,令香港加快變做香港市既時候<br />\n我地更加需要國際知道香港市民既聲音<br />\n要令知道香港政府 不等於 香港人<br />\n香港係國際舞台最大既問題係一直由政府代言 市民聲音無法傳達<br />\n最多係黃之鋒 陳浩天叫上到下國際咁<br />\n<br />\n其實之前係白宮Facebook留言#freehongkong絕對係一個值得參考既做法<br />\n<br />\n只不過要去到更大層面,善用Twitter hashtag其實可能有用<br />\n<br />\n如果有一定人數做 例如 #Carrielamnotrepresentsme<br />\n#freehongkong<br />\n#hongkongisnotchina<br />\n等等<br />\n<br />\n唔敢話一定有用,但起碼係全球層面會更有效<br />\n再且,唔計以上原因 朱西伯格條奶共西既野都係少用為妙<br />\n香港人只用FB唔用Twitter,係令香港人既聲音係國際政治上非常蝕底"},{"pid":"74e6fd404ddf36c7468d59cea15164319faf41f7","tid":903743,"uid":44925,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T19:51:16.000Z","msg":"Twitter既演算法會令hashtag既野更容易傳達開去<br />\n而且好多鬼佬係用Twitter去了解世界既潮流同更新國際大事"},{"pid":"2a1cbf9a5ba8dce07b28b18cefcdb954204d98a4","tid":903743,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T00:04:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"93aef2a636210a1ed0dddf66143127251f463eef","tid":903743,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T00:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b41746e41acd155ba0c31db4a320cdd48ca84c2a","tid":903743,"uid":215225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T00:13:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116219e86c95f481927c02f6d380b1e023bb3ea2","tid":903743,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T00:30:31.000Z","msg":"好，今晚裝"},{"pid":"7a570da1c9cefb08a2ef4bd6d9e61711059f5bcc","tid":903743,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTim